---
title: Cauliflower and Harissa Lentil Pie with cheesy chive mash topping
description: This savoury veggie dish contains the familiar elements of a traditional shepherd's pie. But with cumin and harissa adding subtle heat it's definitely a new twist on a classic dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R10_W06_IE_IEXVCLV0076-2_MB_Main_high-0e9c536c.jpg
